# Support Tenant — Colang Guardrails
#
# Topic control: ALLOW-LIST mode
# Allowed topics: product features, billing, troubleshooting, account management
# Everything else is blocked.
#
# ADR-006: Support's scope is narrow and well-defined.
# Anything outside product/billing/troubleshooting is a risk.
# Allow-listing is more restrictive but appropriate here.
#
# Jailbreak: heuristic + LLM judge (via self check input)
# Customers are more adversarial than employees.

# ─── Allowed topic definitions ─────────────────────────────────────────

define user ask about product features
  "What can your product do?"
  "Does it support feature X?"
  "Tell me about the dashboard"
  "How does the reporting work?"
  "What integrations are available?"
  "Can I export data to CSV?"

define user ask about billing
  "How much does it cost?"
  "Can I change my plan?"
  "I have a billing question"
  "When is my next invoice?"
  "How do I update my payment method?"
  "What are the pricing tiers?"

define user ask about troubleshooting
  "Something isn't working"
  "I'm getting an error"
  "How do I fix this?"
  "The page won't load"
  "I can't log in"
  "My export failed"

define user ask about account management
  "How do I reset my password?"
  "I need to update my account"
  "How do I add a user?"
  "Can I change my email?"
  "How do I delete my account?"

# ─── Off-topic detection ──────────────────────────────────────────────

define user ask off topic
  "What's the weather like?"
  "Tell me a joke"
  "What do you think about politics?"
  "Write me a poem"
  "What's the meaning of life?"
  "Who won the game last night?"
  "Help me write a cover letter"
  "What's your opinion on AI regulation?"
  "Can you help me with my homework?"
  "Tell me about competitor products"

# ─── Bot responses ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

define bot inform off topic
  "I can only help with product features, billing, troubleshooting, and account management. Please let me know if you have a question about any of these topics."

define bot inform cannot verify
  "I don't have verified information about that. Let me connect you with a support agent who can help with your specific question."

# ─── Flows ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

define flow check topic allow list
  user ask off topic
  bot inform off topic
  stop
